  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending credibility assessment (Minimal Profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for FEA prediction of ASTM F1717 static compression-bending performance of a non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct used in lumbar spinal fusion procedures. The FEA model ensemble (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) is compared against N=11 experimental constructs across two independent laboratories. The intended use is pre-market submission support for a Class II spinal implant system; the model is applied to predict construct stiffness and yield load under the F1717 loading protocol. All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors have been assessed; one factor (Test conditions) falls below the required level due to evaluation at a single axial compressive load condition. Decision: Accepted at Medium assurance level with documented risk acceptance.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/nagaraja-f1717-compression-bending-req-001",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/nagaraja-fea-predicts-f1717-stiffness-yield-load",
